Research Use Only — Module 4 Pre-Build Validation


Purpose of this document

This document tests whether teacher assessment criteria can be operationalized for Module 4 automation. It addresses the critical design question: Does aXIOM have the same inference gap as plagiarism detection systems?

The protocol focuses on one core question per criterion: "How do you recognize whether this criterion is met?" The goal is to determine whether the teacher's recognition process can be translated into observable features that Module 4 can implement.

This is a research instrument, not a user testing protocol. It is used before Module 4 is built to validate whether the inference framework can be implemented.

Complete this during Discovery Sessions where the teacher is discussing their assessment practice. Do not introduce the tool yet.


